      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：臨床現場の「あるある」問題提起",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#14b8a6}.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:0 80px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:30px;line-height:1.4}.alert-box{border-left:5px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:28px 32px;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;margin-bottom:20px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.8}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.5}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 2/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><p class=\"section-label\">起 ── 問題提起</p><h2>「GLP-1って痩せる注射でしょ？」</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>SNSで「痩せ薬」として拡散<br>美容クリニックでの適応外処方が社会問題化<br>しかし、本当の価値は「体重減少」ではない</p></div><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>GLP-1受容体は膵臓だけでなく<br><strong style=\"color:#2dd4bf\">心臓・腎臓・肝臓・脳</strong>にも広く存在する</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
