      "title": "多臓器保護エビデンスの全貌",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：4つの大規模RCTのデータ一覧",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#0a1a1a;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:0 60px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:30px;color:#0d4a4a}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:22px 26px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-label{font-size:16px;color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}.card-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:6px}.card-detail{font-size:20px;color:#475569;line-height:1.5}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.5}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 3/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><p class=\"section-label\">承 ── エビデンス</p><h2>多臓器保護エビデンスの全貌</h2><div class=\"grid\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-label\">心血管 ── SELECT試験</div><div class=\"card-num\">MACE -20%</div><div class=\"card-detail\">非糖尿病肥満17,604例<br>HR 0.80 (NEJM 2023)</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-label\">腎臓 ── FLOW試験</div><div class=\"card-num\">腎イベント -24%</div><div class=\"card-detail\">T2D+CKD 3,533例<br>HR 0.76 (NEJM 2024)</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-label\">肝臓 ── ESSENCE試験</div><div class=\"card-num\">NASH消退 62.9%</div><div class=\"card-detail\">MASH+F2-F3線維化<br>vs プラセボ34.3% (NEJM 2025)</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-label\">睡眠 ── SURMOUNT-OSA</div><div class=\"card-num\">AHI -25~30/h</div><div class=\"card-detail\">中等~重症OSA+肥満<br>約50%が寛解 (NEJM 2024)</div></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
