      "style": "light",
      "content": "結：臨床シナリオ別の処方判断",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#0a1a1a;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:0 60px}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:24px;color:#0d4a4a}.scenario{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:18px 24px;margin-bottom:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px}.scenario-icon{font-size:26px;min-width:36px;color:#14b8a6;font-weight:900}.scenario-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.5}.scenario-drug{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.5}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 5/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><p class=\"section-label\">結 ── 実践</p><h2>臨床シナリオ別の処方判断</h2><div class=\"scenario\"><span class=\"scenario-icon\">1</span><span class=\"scenario-text\"><strong>肥満+T2D+CKD</strong> → <span class=\"scenario-drug\">セマグルチド</span>追加（SGLT2iと併用OK）</span></div><div class=\"scenario\"><span class=\"scenario-icon\">2</span><span class=\"scenario-text\"><strong>肥満+HFpEF</strong> → <span class=\"scenario-drug\">セマグルチド2.4mg</span>で症状改善</span></div><div class=\"scenario\"><span class=\"scenario-icon\">3</span><span class=\"scenario-text\"><strong>肥満+MASH(F2-F3)</strong> → <span class=\"scenario-drug\">セマグルチド2.4mg</span>（FDA承認済）</span></div><div class=\"scenario\"><span class=\"scenario-icon\">4</span><span class=\"scenario-text\"><strong>肥満+重症OSA</strong> → <span class=\"scenario-drug\">チルゼパチド</span>（CPAP併用で最適化）</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
